description: Store canonical skills under skills and symlink into .cursor/skills
alwaysApply: true
---

# Skill Layout

- Keep the source of truth for repo-local skills under `skills/{skill-name}/`.
- When a Cursor-discoverable copy is needed, create a directory symlink in `.cursor/skills/{skill-name}` pointing to `skills/{skill-name}`.
- Do not duplicate skill files between `skills/` and `.cursor/skills/`.
- Prefer concise skill names without prefixes like `dmf-` unless the user explicitly asks to keep the prefix.
